name: baggage bidder
description:
Every day thousands of baggage travels by busses, trains or airplanes.
Some of them gets lost and if unclaimed sold in public auctions where bidder like you can buy them.
And nobody knows what treasures you might find in these bags:
just an empty bag, nothing but old worthless socks or rear expensive antiquary or even gold bar...

note that this is game not an actual auctions
